* ''Caesar Antichrist''
* [[Ubu Roi|''Ubu the King'' (Ubu Roi)]]
* ''Ubu Cuckolded (Ubu cocu)''
* ''Ubu Bound (Ubu enchaíné)''

===Novels===
* ''[[Supermale (novel)|The Supermale]] (Le Surmâle)''
* ''[[Messalina (novel)|Messalina]] (Messaline)''
