* ''[[Days and Nights (novel)]] (Les Jours et les nuits )''

===Other notable works===
* Short story, ''The Passion Considered as an Uphill Bicycle Race'' (''La Passion considérée comme course de côte''), has been widely circulated and imitated, notably by [[J.G. Ballard]], and [[Robert Anton Wilson]]

