      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox person
|name=Amalric I of Jerusalem
| image =Amalrich1.jpg
| image_size = 230px
| alt = Amalric I The King
| spouse =[[Agnes of Courtenay]]&lt;br /&gt;[[Maria Komnene, Queen of Jerusalem|Maria Komnene]]
