* Lippi-Green, Rosina. (1997). ''English with an accent: Language, ideology, and discrimination in the United States''. New York: Routedge.
* MacNeil, Robert; &amp; Cran, William. (2005). ''Do you speak American?: A companion to the PBS television series.'' New York: Nan A. Talese, Doubleday.
