{{Infobox scientist
| name              = Sir Alexander Fleming
| image             = Nobelpristagare Fleming Midi.jpg
| image_size        = 300px
| caption           = Fleming (centre) receiving the Nobel prize from King [[Gustaf V of Sweden|Gustaf V]] of Sweden (right), 1945
